A '''capstone course''', also known as '''capstone unit''' or a '''senior thesis''' or '''senior seminar''' serves as the culminating and usually integrative experience of an educational program.<ref name="FordFord2006">{{cite book|author1=Marcus Ford|author2=Marcus Peter Ford|title=Beyond the Modern University: Toward a C|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=lRc3f2gjCJYC&pg=PA44|year=2006|publisher=IAP|isbn=978-1-59311-405-3|page=44}}</ref> A capstone course, module, project, subject, or unit in the higher education context may also be referred to as a capstone experience, senior seminar (in the U.S.), or final year project or dissertation (more common in the U.K.).
The term derives from the final decorative [[Coping (architecture)|coping]] or "cap-stone" used to complete a building or monument. In higher education, the term has been in common use in the USA since the mid-twentieth century, although there is evidence that it was in use as early as the late 1800s.<ref>{{cite book|authors=Hauhart, R. & Grahe, J. |date=2015|title=Designing and teaching undergraduate capstone courses|location= San-Francisco|publisher= Jossey-Bass}}</ref> It has gradually been gaining currency in other countries, particularly where attention has focused on student outcomes and employability in undergraduate studies.{{cn|date=October 2017}} National grant projects in Australia<ref>{{cite web|website=businesscapstones.edu|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160109155709/http://businesscapstones.edu.au/ |title=Business Capstones|location=Australia}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://eprints.qut.edu.au/64249/ |website=eprints.qut.edu.au|title=Curriculum renewal in legal education: Capstone experiences in law|location=Australia}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.capstonecurriculum.com.au/ |website=capstonecurriculum.com/edu|title=Capstones across disciplines and the capstone network|location=Australia}}</ref> and the U.K. have further raised the profile of the capstone experience.<ref>{{cite web|website=heacademy.ac.uk|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170113163805/https://www.heacademy.ac.uk/project/rethinking-final-year-projects-and-dissertations-creative-honours-and-capstone-projects |title=Rethinking final-year projects and dissertations: Creative honours and capstone projects|location=U.K.}}</ref>
